Feature:: Add hours
    Description: Add hours worked on an
    activity in a project
    Actor: Employee
# Main scenario
Scenario: Add hours worked for an
activity in a project that the employee
is part of
    Given there is a project
    And employee with ID "mkr" is logged in
    And employee is part of project
    And employee is not the project manager
    And project has the activity "Add feature"
    When add "5" hours to "Add feature" activity in project
    Then "5" hours have been added to activity "Add feature" in the project
# Alternative scenario
Scenario: Add hours worked helping an
colleague with an activity.
    Given there is a project
    And employee with ID "mkr" is logged in
    And employee is not part of project
    And employee is not the project manager
    When add "5" hours to "Add feature" activity in project
    Then "5" hours have been added to activity "Add feature" in the project